{"tid":2378484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城大網上畢業禮將經 bilibili 等直播　 學生會質疑不合適","createTime":"2021-01-24T13:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T14:24:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3158a19643e838495024b32eb2d5392555fc2c53","tid":2378484,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T13:30:50.000Z","msg":"疫情之下，不少大學改在網上舉行畢業禮，城市大學將於 2 月 1 日起陸續舉行網上畢業禮，其中一個直播平台為內地網站 bilibili，引起討論。城大學生會署理會長林穎曦表示，明白校方要顧及中國學生，但該網站以動漫為主，亦有留言「彈幕」等功能，擔心是否適合作畢業禮。《立場》正就事件向城大查詢。<br />\n<br />\n據城大的畢業禮網頁顯示，虛擬畢業禮將按學院分為 9 場，由 2 月 1 日起一連四日舉行，典禮將透過美國網站 Vimeo 及內地網站 bilibili 直播。<br />\n<br />\n城大學生會署理會長林穎曦向《立場》表示，理解校方要顧及中國學生，讓他們亦能參與畢業禮，但坦言自己不太熟悉 bilibili，感覺該網站以動漫為主，亦容許觀眾發「彈幕」，在影片上出現觀眾的留言，擔心是否適合用作畢業禮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%A6%AE%E5%B0%87%E7%B6%93-bilibili-%E7%AD%89%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E9%81%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%25B6%2593-bilibili-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%2581%25A9%2F&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=64d6ef63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%25B6%2593-bilibili-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%2581%25A9%2F&h=e8180559\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%9F%8E%E5%A4%A7%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%95%A2%E6%A5